<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=U2&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h3>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
